divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: At around 10.45 gmt i was out setting up my table and this craft zoomed right by. As far as i cold see it was one craft but i may be wrong. There were four lights and two of them kept changing colours. They span around in a circle togother and it was all going so fast. It made a kind of "wooooooooo" noise as it went of. I only saw for about 10 seconds. Thanks.
